header.name: Andrews Helicopters (resources) v1.1.17
header.description: Helicopters extracted and improved by MRxSIR from 'Survival Helicopters v1.5' by yimmplay. §aInstructions: Craft helicopters, nitro, and repair kits in the crafting table. Level 3 weapon smith villagers sell fuel and also helicopters. You'll need to craft a key (need blackstone from the Nether). Use the key to start the helicopter from the outside (interact with it outside). §eChinook: Load/Unload Villager tools. Load other nearby mobs with boat on Chinook, unload using torch.
